#: ../../../logging.rst:8
msgid "Setting Up Logging"
msgstr "設定日誌記錄"

#: ../../../logging.rst:10
msgid ""
"*discord.py* logs errors and debug information via the :mod:`logging` python "
"module. In order to streamline this process, the library provides default "
"configuration for the ``discord`` logger when using :meth:`Client.run`. It "
"is strongly recommended that the logging module is configured, as no errors "
"or warnings will be output if it is not set up."
msgstr ""
"*discord.py* 透過 :mod:`logging` Python 模組來記錄錯誤與除錯資訊。為了簡化此"
"流程，程式庫在使用 :meth:`Client.run` 時會為 ``discord`` 日誌記錄器提供預設設"
"定。強烈建議您設定日誌模組，因為如果未進行設定，將不會輸出任何錯誤或警告。"

#: ../../../logging.rst:13
msgid ""
"The default logging configuration provided by the library will print to :"
"data:`sys.stderr` using coloured output. You can configure it to send to a "
"file instead by using one of the built-in :mod:`logging.handlers`, such as :"
"class:`logging.FileHandler`."
msgstr ""
"程式庫提供的預設日誌設定會使用彩色輸出將內容列印到 :data:`sys.stderr`。您也可"
"以改用內建的 :mod:`logging.handlers`（例如 :class:`logging.FileHandler`）將其"
"設定為輸出到檔案。"

#: ../../../logging.rst:15
msgid "This can be done by passing it through :meth:`Client.run`:"
msgstr "這可以透過將其傳遞給 :meth:`Client.run` 來完成："

#: ../../../logging.rst:17
msgid ""
"import logging\n"
"\n"
"handler = logging.FileHandler(filename='discord.log', encoding='utf-8', "
"mode='w')\n"
"\n"
"# Assume client refers to a discord.Client subclass...\n"
"client.run(token, log_handler=handler)"
msgstr ""
"import logging\n"
"\n"
"handler = logging.FileHandler(filename='discord.log', encoding='utf-8', "
"mode='w')\n"
"\n"
"# 假設 client 指向一個 discord.Client 子類別...\n"
"client.run(token, log_handler=handler)"

#: ../../../logging.rst:26
msgid ""
"You can also disable the library's logging configuration completely by "
"passing ``None``:"
msgstr "您也可以透過傳遞 ``None`` 來完全停用程式庫的日誌設定："

#: ../../../logging.rst:28
msgid "client.run(token, log_handler=None)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../logging.rst:33
msgid ""
"Likewise, configuring the log level to ``logging.DEBUG`` is also possible:"
msgstr "同樣地，也可以將日誌層級設定為 ``logging.DEBUG``："

#: ../../../logging.rst:35
msgid ""
"import logging\n"
"\n"
"handler = logging.FileHandler(filename='discord.log', encoding='utf-8', "
"mode='w')\n"
"\n"
"# Assume client refers to a discord.Client subclass...\n"
"client.run(token, log_handler=handler, log_level=logging.DEBUG)"
msgstr ""
"import logging\n"
"\n"
"handler = logging.FileHandler(filename='discord.log', encoding='utf-8', "
"mode='w')\n"
"\n"
"# 假設 client 指向一個 discord.Client 子類別...\n"
"client.run(token, log_handler=handler, log_level=logging.DEBUG)"

#: ../../../logging.rst:44
msgid ""
"This is recommended, especially at verbose levels such as ``DEBUG``, as "
"there are a lot of events logged and it would clog the stderr of your "
"program."
msgstr ""
"建議這樣做，特別是在 ``DEBUG`` 等詳細層級下，因為會記錄大量事件，若輸出到 "
"stderr 可能會淹沒您程式的終端輸出。"

#: ../../../logging.rst:46
msgid ""
"If you want the logging configuration the library provides to affect all "
"loggers rather than just the ``discord`` logger, you can pass "
"``root_logger=True`` inside :meth:`Client.run`:"
msgstr ""
"如果您希望程式庫提供的日誌設定影響所有日誌記錄器，而不僅是 ``discord`` 日誌記"
"錄器，可以在 :meth:`Client.run` 中傳遞 ``root_logger=True``："

#: ../../../logging.rst:48
msgid "client.run(token, log_handler=handler, root_logger=True)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../logging.rst:52
msgid ""
"If you want to setup logging using the library provided configuration "
"without using :meth:`Client.run`, you can use :func:`discord.utils."
"setup_logging`:"
msgstr ""
"如果您想在不使用 :meth:`Client.run` 的情況下使用程式庫提供的設定來設置日誌，"
"可以使用 :func:`discord.utils.setup_logging`："

#: ../../../logging.rst:54
msgid ""
"import discord\n"
"\n"
"discord.utils.setup_logging()\n"
"\n"
"# or, for example\n"
"discord.utils.setup_logging(level=logging.INFO, root=False)"
msgstr ""
"import discord\n"
"\n"
"discord.utils.setup_logging()\n"
"\n"
"# 或者，例如\n"
"discord.utils.setup_logging(level=logging.INFO, root=False)"

#: ../../../logging.rst:63
msgid ""
"More advanced setups are possible with the :mod:`logging` module. The "
"example below configures a rotating file handler that outputs DEBUG output "
"for everything the library outputs, except for HTTP requests:"
msgstr ""
"使用 :mod:`logging` 模組可以進行更進階的設定。以下範例設定了一個循環檔案處理"
"器，對程式庫輸出的所有內容（HTTP 請求除外）輸出 DEBUG 層級的記錄："

#: ../../../logging.rst:65
msgid ""
"import discord\n"
"import logging\n"
"import logging.handlers\n"
"\n"
"logger = logging.getLogger('discord')\n"
"logger.setLevel(logging.DEBUG)\n"
"logging.getLogger('discord.http').setLevel(logging.INFO)\n"
"\n"
"handler = logging.handlers.RotatingFileHandler(\n"
"    filename='discord.log',\n"
"    encoding='utf-8',\n"
"    maxBytes=32 * 1024 * 1024,  # 32 MiB\n"
"    backupCount=5,  # Rotate through 5 files\n"
")\n"
"dt_fmt = '%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S'\n"
"formatter = logging.Formatter('[{asctime}] [{levelname:<8}] {name}: "
"{message}', dt_fmt, style='{')\n"
"handler.setFormatter(formatter)\n"
"logger.addHandler(handler)\n"
"\n"
"# Assume client refers to a discord.Client subclass...\n"
"# Suppress the default configuration since we have our own\n"
"client.run(token, log_handler=None)"
msgstr ""
"import discord\n"
"import logging\n"
"import logging.handlers\n"
"\n"
"logger = logging.getLogger('discord')\n"
"logger.setLevel(logging.DEBUG)\n"
"logging.getLogger('discord.http').setLevel(logging.INFO)\n"
"\n"
"handler = logging.handlers.RotatingFileHandler(\n"
"    filename='discord.log',\n"
"    encoding='utf-8',\n"
"    maxBytes=32 * 1024 * 1024,  # 32 MiB\n"
"    backupCount=5,  # 在 5 個檔案之間循環\n"
")\n"
"dt_fmt = '%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S'\n"
"formatter = logging.Formatter('[{asctime}] [{levelname:<8}] {name}: "
"{message}', dt_fmt, style='{')\n"
"handler.setFormatter(formatter)\n"
"logger.addHandler(handler)\n"
"\n"
"# 假設 client 指向一個 discord.Client 子類別...\n"
"# 抑制預設設定，因為我們已有自己的設定\n"
"client.run(token, log_handler=None)"

#: ../../../logging.rst:91
msgid ""
"For more information, check the documentation and tutorial of the :mod:"
"`logging` module."
msgstr "如需更多資訊，請查閱 :mod:`logging` 模組的文件與教學。"

#: ../../../logging.rst:95
msgid "The library now provides a default logging configuration."
msgstr "此程式庫現在提供預設的日誌設定。"
